Services.
    - Services will share the "common business logic" to the controllers.

    - we have two types of services.

        1.Predefined Services

        2.Custom Services


Custom Services.
    - The Services Developed by the developer Called as Custom Services.

    - We Can Create Custom Services in five ways.

        1.provider()

        2.factory()

        3.value()

        4.constant()

        5.service()